<br>
Althought I agree with provoke using LOW endu its even more unbalanced but my comparison was sword vs axe and it still showed a diff.<br>
<br>
Now as far as our class being balanced again I say the class rocks......but slowly and surely everybody keeps saying were balanced were balanced and  we rock we rock...and POOF the whiners make this unbalanced.<br>
I mean midgard is missing out on alot of features in realm comparisons....<br>
We are the underdogs and have been and most people that play Midgurd want to play for the fun...mostly.<br>
<br>
They have been mentioned before...<br>
Battle Healer<br>
endu regen<br>
Sos<br>
Group purge<br>
etc etc etc<br>
3 ressing classes<br>
<br>
Again if you compare us to paladins......they can outdamage us and can res and wear plate..2 skill point for more abilities.<br>
If you compare to the other song classes they have higher defense...same armor...same shouts PLUS not only ae mezzes but now getting insta mezzes in one realm.....<br>
<br>
If we are a cross of both types thats where we get screwed.....we dont get the loving in the damage area to be more like paladins and we dont get the ae mez lines that the other song classes get.<br>
Thats my biggest beef....and to be honest as every prior game the squeky wheel gets the oil.<br>
Again I enjoy the class greatly but if we keep sitting back saying we like our class sooo much mythic will continue the loving to all the classes whining and we will end up screwed end game.<br>
Hell even to make us more like paladins they can even simply remove the EDU usage from cvhants and the damage would balance out cause we could use chants without losing damage using styles the whole fight.<br>
<br>
We have one class in midgard that has the insta mez and happens to be one of two healing classes that happenes to drop like a caster and we are in need of.<br>
<br>
Give the skald an Ae mez too all off a sudden healers can heal again<br>
Give SM the Res line and Tada we are much more balanced with the other realms.<br>
Give me a reason to turn off my speed line to use MEZ line...thats what the other song classes get.<br>
<br>
If we are compared to paladins then remove the ENDU usage from our chants so that damage is in addition to stlyes damage that alone would balance out.<br>
<br>
If we are song compared then give us the AE mez or AE stun and we fall in line with them.<br>
I prefer the later cause then it would balance the three classes<br>
<br>
Skald Advantage better tank<br>
Minstrel Advantage Hide/sos<br>
Bard advantage Res/heal lines<br>
<br>
All with Ae stun or mez line of some sort<br>
I honestly believe that it could be requested and rewarded only if we actually stood behind it.<br>
but if everyone keep sayng we are balanced the other classes will continue to move further and further away.<br>
<br>
Lets face it Mythic uses albion classes to base the other realms.<br>
Minstrels have it all. Now they made bards a bit more like minstrels and where are we? Still happy????<br>
what little bit better of a tank we are doesnt measure up to the AE stun/mez lines.<br>
Im glad bards got what they got.......but I dont believe it should stop there we should too....that way the song classes stay relatively similar with there own special class abilities.<br>
